# Agent profile — the LOCAL Supabase stack only (`supabase start`), loaded by
# `npm run dev:agent` (vite --mode agent) and the harness scripts.
#
# Committed on purpose: these are the Supabase CLI's public local-development
# default keys, identical for every local project. Nothing here is a secret.
# Real project credentials must never go in this file — every harness
# component refuses non-localhost URLs.
